Add/remove hooks
================

To add a hook:

1. add the hook as a Python plugin under `bin/plugins/hook_NAME.py`

2. trigger the `add-package` event for the new hook:

    $ bin/update-debsources(-ng) -vvv --pass none --trigger add-package/NAME

3. add the hook to the `hooks` configuration entry in config(.local).ini

To remove a hook follow the reverse process, but trigger the `rm-package` event
instead.
